The paper presents a method for model-based online reinforcement learning, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also deals with control and decision-making problems, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
